description:
While on your %{ZONE:GARDEN}, grants a buff depending on the current SkyBlock season.
 %{KEYWORD:POINTED_STAR} %{SEASON:SPRING}
  Grants %{VALUE:SEASONAL_FARMING_FORTUNE} %{STAT:FARMING_FORTUNE}.
 %{KEYWORD:POINTED_STAR} %{SEASON:SUMMER}
  Grants %{VALUE:SEASONAL_FARMING_WISDOM} %{STAT:FARMING_WISDOM}.
 %{KEYWORD:POINTED_STAR} %{SEASON:FALL}
  %{KEYWORDS:PEST} spawn %{VALUE:SEASONAL_PEST_CHANCE} more often.
 %{KEYWORD:POINTED_STAR} %{SEASON:WINTER}
  Visitors give %{VALUE:SEASONAL_COPPER} more Copper.

Every %{FORMAT:GREEN}SkyBlock Season%{FORMAT:GRAY}, the %{FORMAT:DARK_PURPLE}Magic 8 Ball %{FORMAT:GRAY}will grant one of the following bonuses:

%{SYMBOL:POINTED_STAR} It is certain.
   %{VALUE:SEASONAL_FARMING_FORTUNE} %{STAT:FARMING_FORTUNE}
   %{VALUE:SEASONAL_FARMING_WISDOM} %{STAT:FARMING_WISDOM}
%{SYMBOL:POINTED_STAR} Reply hazy, try again.
   %{VALUE:SEASONAL_FORAGING_FORTUNE} %{STAT:FORAGING_FORTUNE}
   %{VALUE:SEASONAL_FORAGING_WISDOM} %{STAT:FORAGING_WISDOM}
%{SYMBOL:POINTED_STAR} Don't count on it.
   %{VALUE:SEASONAL_MINING_FORTUNE} %{STAT:MINING_FORTUNE}
   %{VALUE:SEASONAL_MINING_WISDOM} %{STAT:MINING_WISDOM}
%{SYMBOL:POINTED_STAR} As I see it, yes.
   %{VALUE:SEASONAL_FISHING_SPEED} %{STAT:FISHING_SPEED}
   %{VALUE:SEASONAL_FISHING_WISDOM} %{STAT:FISHING_WISDOM}
%{SYMBOL:POINTED_STAR} My sources say no.
   %{VALUE:SEASONAL_STRENGTH} %{STAT:STRENGTH}
   %{VALUE:SEASONAL_COMBAT_WISDOM} %{STAT:COMBAT_WISDOM}
